The paper discusses the challenges of implementing full-duplex communication in mobile devices, which involves advanced circuit and signal processing solutions. This topic is closely related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI), as well as system and control theory (cs.SY). The paper also includes RF measurement results from a complete demonstrator implementation, which involves multimedia (cs.MM) and architecture (cs.AR) aspects.
